  "short_description": "This is a casual game that combines math and basic elimination gameplay. If you're confident in your math skills, give it a try! In the game, you'll decide the direction of all the \"blocks\" and gradually strengthen the \"Blue Legion\" to defeat the evil \"Red Legion.\"",
