  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Here is the translation of the updated text:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This is a casual puzzle game that combines mathematical calculations and basic elimination gameplay. In the game, you can slide the mouse to determine the movement direction of all \"blocks,\" and through repeated decisions, gradually strengthen the \"Blue Legion\" to ultimately defeat the evil \"Red Legion.\"</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay Instructions:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slide the mouse to control the movement of all blocks.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429970/extras/7b89278f49428aaf5194fe8c545bb63a.poster.avif?t=1742901706\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429970/extras/7b89278f49428aaf5194fe8c545bb63a.webm?t=1742901706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blocks of the same color and value can merge to strengthen the legion’s power!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429970/extras/c11cfa8ca7712e187c299f74565352e0.poster.avif?t=1742901706\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429970/extras/c11cfa8ca7712e187c299f74565352e0.webm?t=1742901706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If a block's value is greater than or equal to the enemy’s, it can \"eat\" the enemy and generate a new block.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429970/extras/ebfebec640f060fed609952d04da9988.poster.avif?t=1742901706\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429970/extras/ebfebec640f060fed609952d04da9988.webm?t=1742901706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control your Blue Legion and achieve victory!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429970/extras/5a45f5b4f4838b6e1bc1e3e1311ae524.poster.avif?t=1742901706\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429970/extras/5a45f5b4f4838b6e1bc1e3e1311ae524.webm?t=1742901706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429970/extras/5a45f5b4f4838b6e1bc1e3e1311ae524.mp4?t=1742901706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Here is the translation of the updated text:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This is a casual puzzle game that combines mathematical calculations and basic elimination gameplay. In the game, you can slide the mouse to determine the movement direction of all \"blocks,\" and through repeated decisions, gradually strengthen the \"Blue Legion\" to ultimately defeat the evil \"Red Legion.\"</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay Instructions:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Slide the mouse to control the movement of all blocks.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429970/extras/7b89278f49428aaf5194fe8c545bb63a.poster.avif?t=1742901706\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429970/extras/7b89278f49428aaf5194fe8c545bb63a.webm?t=1742901706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blocks of the same color and value can merge to strengthen the legion’s power!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429970/extras/c11cfa8ca7712e187c299f74565352e0.poster.avif?t=1742901706\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429970/extras/c11cfa8ca7712e187c299f74565352e0.webm?t=1742901706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If a block's value is greater than or equal to the enemy’s, it can \"eat\" the enemy and generate a new block.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429970/extras/ebfebec640f060fed609952d04da9988.poster.avif?t=1742901706\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429970/extras/ebfebec640f060fed609952d04da9988.webm?t=1742901706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control your Blue Legion and achieve victory!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429970/extras/5a45f5b4f4838b6e1bc1e3e1311ae524.poster.avif?t=1742901706\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429970/extras/5a45f5b4f4838b6e1bc1e3e1311ae524.webm?t=1742901706\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429970/extras/5a45f5b4f4838b6e1bc1e3e1311ae524.mp4?t=1742901706\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
